rring something on the ESP P4 at 200kb/s recently</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1454018729779138600", "author": "🦦 Hilton Travis SMBI", "author_handle": "hiltontravissmbi", "user_id": "1430489846090043482", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1430489846090043482/d40eb19b82a2cb5fc68c6c0bc7093cc7.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, December 26, 2025 2:51 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-12-26 2:51 a.m.", "text": "https://discord.com/channels/1343693475589263471/1391673743453192242/1452692944506196021", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve><a href=\"https://discord.com/channels/1343693475589263471/1391673743453192242/1452692944506196021\" onclick=\"scrollToMessage(event, '1452692944506196021')\">https://discord.com/channels/1343693475589263471/1391673743453192242/1452692944506196021</a></span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "<div class=chatlog__reply><img class=chatlog__reply-avatar src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/762997280323928065/9d08f8b053d600d80e4890599e4e4cc4.png?size=512\" alt=Avatar loading=lazy><div class=chatlog__reply-author title=pelgraine>pelgraine</div><div class=chatlog__reply-content><span class=chatlog__reply-link onclick=\"scrollToMessage(event,'1453950799880392744')\"> No idea how I&#39;d find the video again, it was somewhere here in the server </span> <span class=chatlog__reply-edited-timestamp title=\"Thursday, December 25, 2025 10:21 p.m.\">(edited)</span></div></div>", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1454024884874121236", "author": "pelgraine", "author_handle": "pelgraine", "user_id": "762997280323928065", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/762997280323928065/9d08f8b053d600d80e4890599e4e4cc4.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, December 26, 2025 3:15 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-12-26 3:15 a.m.", "text": "dude this is awesome", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>dude this is awesome</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "<div class=chatlog__reply><img class=chatlog__reply-avatar src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/826818523334574131/e5da78658529d9d6cf324a2c50fb3e47.png?size=512\" alt=Avatar loading=lazy><div class=chatlog__reply-author style=color:rgb(231,76,60) title=andykirby9915>andykirby</div><div class=chatlog__reply-content><span class=chatlog__reply-link onclick=\"scrollToMessage(event,'1454022097302192129')\"> <em>Click to see attachment</em> <span>🖼️</span> </span></div></div>", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1454199797086027946", "author": "awhite", "author_handle": "awhite_", "user_id": "796745893252169818", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/796745893252169818/d7d4873bdc4f6063807e07e4b4718a68.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, December 26, 2025 2:50 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-12-26 2:50 p.m.", "text": "I doubt you can transmit any meaningful amount of data without exceeding the legally permitted duty cycle.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>I doubt you can transmit any meaningful amount of data without exceeding the legally permitted duty cycle.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=thumbsup><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=👍 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f44d.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>3</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1454264524764086324", "author": "H3JA", "author_handle": "hejali", "user_id": "540167556443406338", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/540167556443406338/f2de57fe58dad5b846bf84187c43b502.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, December 26, 2025 7:08 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-12-26 7:08 p.m.", "text": "He did transmit that file very fast, the duty cycle is 6 minutes per hour", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>He did transmit that file very fast, the duty cycle is 6 minutes per hour</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=thumbsup><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=👍 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f44d.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "<div class=chatlog__reply><img class=chatlog__reply-avatar src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/796745893252169818/d7d4873bdc4f6063807e07e4b4718a68.png?size=512\" alt=Avatar loading=lazy><div class=chatlog__reply-author title=awhite_>awhite</div><div class=chatlog__reply-content><span class=chatlog__reply-link onclick=\"scrollToMessage(event,'1454199797086027946')\"> I doubt you can transmit any meaningful amount of data without exceeding the legally permitted duty cycle. </span></div></div>", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1454341831914684608", "author": "pelgraine", "author_handle": "pelgraine", "user_id": "762997280323928065", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/762997280323928065/9d08f8b053d600d80e4890599e4e4cc4.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Saturday, December 27, 2025 12:15 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-12-27 12:15 a.m.", "text": "Same duty cycle doesn’t necessarily apply everywhere, no? We have a lot more leeway here in Australia than in the EU or elsewhere as far as I know", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Same duty cycle doesn’t necessarily apply everywhere, no? We have a lot more leeway here in Australia than in the EU or elsewhere as far as I know</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1454502672177561724", "author": "Bullit", "author_handle": "bullitfx", "user_id": "349251101322641414", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/349251101322641414/19e834d8c8a13793c83c3b373bfee57f.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Saturday, December 27, 2025 10:54 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-12-27 10:54 a.m.", "text": "Unfortunatly, i live in a country which have Duty Cycle (Switzerland) and i already see (at least in my head) that such a feature would end up being used for a lot of garbage. Many „features“ i see makes me concerned, if implemented, that Meshcore could end like Meshtastic. And Meshcore works so fu**ing well that i wouldnt want it to end like Meshtastic… at least, this is my personal opinion.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Unfortunatly, i live in a country which have Duty Cycle (Switzerland) and i already see (at least in my head) that such a feature would end up being used for a lot of garbage. Many „features“ i see makes me concerned, if implemented, that Meshcore could end like Meshtastic. And Meshcore works so fu**ing well that i wouldnt want it to end like Meshtastic… at least, this is my personal opinion.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=100><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=💯 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f4af.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>3</span></div><div class=chatlog__reaction title=beers><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=🍻 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f37b.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}]}